data.description: TAKE ADVANTAGE OF A $5k SELLER CREDIT TO COVER POTENTIAL CLOSING COSTS OR INTEREST BUYDOWN. Escape to the serene beauty of Walton, Oregon with this exceptional property. Nestled on 4.47 acres of picturesque landscape, this 3- bedroom, 1-bathroom home offers a harmonious blend of natural tranquility and modern comforts. Situated alongside a tranquil creek, the property provides a unique waterfront experience, allowing you to immerse yourself in the soothing sounds of nature. The expansive 4.47 acres offers ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, and relaxation, making it a haven for those seeking a peaceful retreat. Recent upgrades have been thoughtfully integrated into the property, ensuring both convenience and sustainability. A brand-new septic system, installed in 2021. The innovative grey water system for house water contributes to eco-friendly practices, while all other water usage is efficiently processed through the septic tank. Adding to the property's allure is a newly constructed greenhouse, providing a dedicated space for cultivating plants and indulging in gardening passions. Inside the home, new wall insulation guarantees year-round comfort, while the brand-new roof, installed by a contractor in 2020, offers peace of mind and protection against the elements. The year 2021 also saw the addition of a ductless system, ensuring optimal heating and cooling throughout the home. The centerpiece of comfort is the wood stove, meticulously crafted by Migelys contractors in 2015. Upon entering the home, you'll find a FULLY FURNISHED home. With the exception of bedroom shelves & storage tubs, and the brand-new Husqvarna lawn mower, everything you need is included to seamlessly settle into your new abode, but not reflected In price and value.
